Bundle/Delivery version 0.01
============================

This Bundle will install all the modules needed to run the
web-publishing, community- management and story-weaving applications
Delivery and Tapestry, which are available from www.spanner.org/software.

It will install this lot:

  * Apache::Constants
  * Apache::Request
  * Apache::Util
  * Class::DBI::Factory
  * Date::Calc
  * Date::Simple
  * Email::Valid
  * File::Headerinfo
  * File::NCopy;
  * HTML::Entities
  * HTML::Tagfilter
  * Imager
  * Mail::Sendmail
  * Template
  * Term::Prompt
  * Text::CSV

If you have any questions, suggestions or objections, do write to wross@cpan.org.